gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.binding.io

  • Packages that use gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.binding.io 
    Package Description
    gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.binding
    The core implementation of the metaschema binding framework.
    gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.binding.io
    Provides core functionality for reading and writing instance data to and from bound objects.
    gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.binding.io.json
    Supports reading and writing JSON instance data.
    gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.binding.io.xml
    Supports reading and writing XML instance data.
    gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.binding.io.yaml
    Supports reading and writing YAML instance data.
    gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.binding.model
    Provides the core implementation of the Metaschema model (gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.model.common) represented as Java class annotations (gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.binding.model.annotations).
    gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.model.testing  
    gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.model.testing.xmlbeans  
    gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.model.testing.xmlbeans.handler  
  • Classes in gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.binding.io used by gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.binding 
    Class Description
    BindingException
    Used to report exceptional conditions related to processing bound objects.
    Format
    Selections of serialization formats.
    IBoundLoader
    A common interface for loading Metaschema based instance resources.
    IDeserializer
    Implementations of this interface are able to read structured data into a bound object instance of the parameterized type.
    ISerializer
    Implementations of this interface are able to write data in a bound object instance of the parameterized type to a structured data format.
